|-------|-------|-------|
| `--bg` | `#F8F9FA` | Page background |
| `--fg` | `#1A1A1B` | Primary text |
| `--fg-muted` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text |
| `--accent` | `#4361EE` | Links, glows, gradient |
| `--glass-bg` | `rgba(248,249,250,0.72)` | Navbar backdrop |
