| `--ease-out-expo` | cubic-bezier | GSAP animation curve |

---

## Smooth Scroll + GSAP Sync

Lenis uses its own RAF loop, which calls `ScrollTrigger.update()` on every tick — ensuring scroll-triggered GSAP animations fire at the correct scroll position without drift.

```
Lenis RAF → lenis.raf(time) → lenis.on("scroll", ScrollTrigger.update)
```

